g.title: j724394717
g.text: Esa gata, that freaky mutant cat
Keeps looking at my panquecitos like they're lunch

g.title: j1525899982
g.text: You mean Kalymos? I'll make sure she leaves your rats alone.

g.title: j2643614543
g.text: That thing is entrati's pet not yours
It looks at me just like he did

g.title: j1936004579
g.text: That thing is entrati's pet not yours
It looks at me just like he did

g.title: j222261622
g.text: And how does she look at you?

g.title: j3627754368
g.text: She's a kavat, Lettie, not a person.

g.title: j96559599
g.text: Like she's trying to figure out how to eat ME
Like one of those cavia you told me about
With too much intelligence behind those eyes

g.title: j3405874841
g.text: Like she's trying to figure out how to eat ME
With too much intelligence behind those eyes
Does the future have smart animals?

g.title: j3426830713
g.text: You told me about the cavia
Those poor animals that cabrón gave intelligence to and abandoned?!

g.title: j4139229674
g.text: Esa gata, it seems too smart to me
Looks at me with human intelligence
Does the future have smart animals?

g.title: j898424303
g.text: Those poor animals that cabrón gave intelligence to and abandoned?!
How do you know she isn't one, too?!

g.title: j2602156454
g.text: There are the Cavia, who are these lab animals that were sent into the Void and came out intelligent. Well.

g.title: j182987822
g.text: Yes, but - oh, this is going to piss you off already, I can tell.

g.title: j4052159840
g.text: How do you know she isn't one, too?!

g.title: j2444062183
g.text: I mean, she's never said anything.

g.title: j189229700
g.text: I guess I don't really know.

g.title: j571723970
g.text: Entrati is the one who tortured them

g.title: j2190932530
g.text: Does it have to do with entrati?

g.title: j3839194194
g.text: But she spies on us for him I know it

g.title: j2785141095
g.text: Entrati left, and she stayed. I don't think she's still working for him.

g.title: j1859706513
g.text: Do you really think she's spying on us for him? Why?

g.title: j3737732358
g.text: I AM GOING to make that cabrón HURT
Next time I see him I will torture him like he tortured those poor angelitos
And he will NOT like it, I PROMISE you THAT

g.title: j2848667983
g.text: It's exactly that reason why I think she is
He's gone and needs eyes here on us, ¿no?
Don't know why, pero no me gusta

g.title: j330767333
g.text: Not my job to predict a crazy pendejo

g.title: j3335653931
g.text: He took these lab animals and sent them into the Void. They came out with the intelligence of people - it nearly killed them. They're called the Cavia.

g.title: j2848541583
g.text: Either way, she's smart enough to understand "If you mess with Lettie's rats, you sleep outside." Is that good enough?

g.title: j3102507874
g.text: I'm not kicking her out. Even if she's working for Entrati, it's not her fault. She's an animal being loyal to the owner who loves her. I can't be cruel to her.

g.title: j1820215936
g.text: And how are you so sure that this gata mutante is not one of these cavia

g.title: j1651461119
g.text: But if she hurts one of my bebecitos

g.title: j2772015737
g.text: Why did you have to put it like that

g.title: j1749943700
g.text: No me gusta cuando te pasas de listo, babas
She stays but if she hurts one of my bebecitos
